: 0px; z-index: 1; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(225, 224, 224); }

.valueFlipperContainer { position: relative; overflow: hidden; }

h: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: hidden; transiti=

}

  .plansTabs .planTab .planCloud { display: none; }
  .plansTabs .planTab .planLabel { font-size: 15px; }

@keyframes makeProgress99 {=20
  0% { width: 0%; }
  100% { width: 99%; }
}

.progressBarBackground { position: relative; height: 10px; width: 100%; bac=
kground-color: rgb(249, 248, 248); }

.progressBarBackground .progressBar { position: absolute; top: 0px; height:=
 10px; background-color: rgb(68, 112, 153); }

.progressBarBackground .progressBar.autoFiftyFive { animation: 55s ease-out=
 0s 1 normal none running makeProgress99; width: 99%; }

.progressBarBackground .progressBar.autoThirty { animation: 30s ease-out 0s=
 1 normal none running makeProgress99; width: 99%; }

.progressBarBackground .progressBar.autoTwoMinutes { animation: 120s ease-o=
ut 0s 1 normal none running makeProgress99; width: 99%; }

.progressBarBackground .progressBar.done { width: 100%; }

ition-duration: 0.1s; }

ight: 100%; max-width: 100%; overflow: auto; background-color: rgb(252, 252=

.listsOnPageContainer { position: sticky; top: 80px; width: 180px; min-widt=
h: 180px; max-height: calc(-85px + 100vh); overflow-y: auto; margin-right: =
40px; padding-bottom: 50px; }

.listsOnPageContainer .separator { line-height: 1px; height: 1px; border-bo=
ttom: 1px solid rgb(241, 240, 240); }

.listsListing a, .listsListing button { color: inherit; }

.listsListing a:hover, .listsListing button:hover { text-decoration: none; =
}

.listsListing a .showOnHoverOrActive, .listsListing button .showOnHoverOrAc=
tive { display: none; }

.listsListing a:hover, .listsListing button:hover { background-color: rgb(2=
49, 248, 248); }

.listsListing a:hover .showOnHoverOrActive, .listsListing button:hover .sho=
wOnHoverOrActive { display: block; }

.listsListing a.active, .listsListing button.active { background-color: rgb=
(227, 238, 248); }

.listsListing a.active .showOnHoverOrActive, .listsListing button.active .s=
howOnHoverOrActive { display: block; }

.listsListing .listItemContainer { position: relative; background-clip: pad=
ding-box; border-top: 1px solid transparent; border-bottom: 1px solid trans=
parent; }

.listsListing .listItemContainer.dragDropHover { background-color: rgb(253,=
 242, 167); }

.listsListing .listItemContainer.dragDropHover a.active { background-color:=
 inherit; }

.listsListing .listItemContainer.dragDropMoveAbove { border-top-color: hotp=
ink; }

.listsListing .listItemContainer.dragDropMoveBelow + li { border-top-color:=
 hotpink; }

.listsListing .list { display: block; border-radius: 0px; background-color:=
 transparent; width: 100%; text-align: left; padding: 11px 12px 11px 36px; =
cursor: pointer; line-height: 16px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; =
text-overflow: ellipsis; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position:=
 10px center; background-size: 20px 20px; }

.listsListing .list.indent { padding-left: 51px; background-position: 25px =
center; }

.hideHeader .listsOnPageContainer { top: 30px; }

@media screen and (max-width: 1023px) {
  .listsOnPageContainer { display: none; }
}

.periodPicker { padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; }

.usagePeriods { padding: 3px; white-space: nowrap; overflow-x: auto; }

ul.usagePeriods { margin-bottom: 0px; }

ul.usagePeriods li { display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 0px; }

.reportingUnit { font-size: 12px; padding: 4px 8px; background-color: trans=
parent; border-radius: 0px; }

.reportingUnit.active { background-color: rgb(227, 238, 248); }

table.slantTableHeaders { border-collapse: collapse; --table-border-width: =
1px; }

table.slantTableHeaders th.rotate { white-space: nowrap; position: relative=
; }

table.slantTableHeaders th.rotate > div { position: absolute; bottom: 0px; =
left: 0px; background-color: pink; text-align: left; transform: translate(c=
alc(100% - var(--table-border-width) / 2), var(--table-border-width)) rotat=
e(315deg); transform-origin: 0% calc(100% - var(--table-border-width)); wid=
th: 100%; }

table.slantTableHeaders th.rotate > div > span { position: absolute; bottom=
: 0px; left: 0px; border-bottom: var(--table-border-width) solid #e5e4e4; p=
adding-bottom: 7px; }

table.slantTableHeaders td { border-right: var(--table-border-width) solid =
#e5e4e4; min-width: 48px; padding: 10px; vertical-align: middle; }

.gridContainer { display: grid; gap: 20px; grid-template-columns: repeat(au=
to-fit, minmax(190px, 1fr)); grid-auto-rows: max-content; padding: 3px; mar=
gin: -3px; }

.gridItem { background-color: rgb(249, 248, 248); border: 2px solid rgb(249=
, 248, 248); border-radius: 5px; transition: 0.2s; padding: 0px; width: 100=
%; overflow: hidden; text-align: left; }

.gridItem:hover { background-color: rgb(241, 240, 240); border-color: rgb(2=
01, 200, 200); }

.gridItem.current { background-color: rgb(227, 238, 248); border-color: rgb=
(121, 176, 226); }
